Name: Orbital X
About the game: Guide your planet along its orbit! An endless run through stars and galaxies! Fast, challenging, rhythmic and addictive! Game features: • Endless procedural track: the game changes every time you play! • Rhythm-based gameplay: everything moves to the music! • Portals: travel between parallel dimensions! • Solar system: 8 planets to unlock with unique abilities! • Extra: unlock all the achievements and climb the leaderboard! Credits: Soundtrack by Jim Yosef, provided by NCS. Photosensitive seizure warning: The visuals in this game could cause problems to people suffering from photosensitive epilepsy.
